                                    <objectType ana="#object.altar" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/29.html">altar</objectType>
                                    <dimensions>
                                        <height unit="cm">36</height>
                                        <width unit="cm">125</width>
                                        <depth unit="cm">45</depth>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </support>
                                <condition ana="#con"/>
		    </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout><p>The inscription is cut into the stucco in the recess and the letters are painted red. Much of the bottom of the stucco has been damaged. “It is highly likely that there was a third line in the [recessed stucco] panel, and quite possible that there were further lines on a block below.” (Crawford 2011)</p>
